---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Evidence before capital"
  description="Independent quantitative research for systematic traders. We validate trading ideas before they risk capital."
>
  <section style="margin-top:3rem;">
    <h1>Evidence before capital.</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.15rem;max-width:600px;margin-bottom:2rem;">
      Independent research for systematic traders.
      We validate trading ideas before they risk capital
      through forward evidence, concentration analysis,
      execution cost testing and statistical validation.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/research" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.625rem 1.5rem;background:var(--color-text);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9375rem;font-weight:500;">Read Research</a>
      <span style="display:inline-block;padding:0.625rem 1.25rem;color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.875rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:6px;">Coming Soon</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>Alpha Factory Research develops and validates systematic trading hypotheses through a structured pipeline: mechanism discovery, data feasibility, reality check, frozen backtesting, forward evidence collection, and concentration/cost analysis.</p>
    <p>We do not provide trading signals, investment advice, or portfolio management. We publish evidence.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Research Pipeline</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Mechanism Discovery — identify structural market edges</li>
      <li>Data Feasibility Gate — verify obtainable, clean historical data</li>
      <li>Reality Check — test causal chain and economic viability</li>
      <li>Frozen Backtesting — preregistered, no parameter search</li>
      <li>Forward Evidence — prospective paper trading before capital</li>
      <li>Concentration & Cost Audit — verify edge survives execution</li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</Base>
